notes: 'url' and 'tabId options can't both be set together.
The returned 'Window' object contains the 'tabs' property only from version 52 onwards.
From Firefox 86, the focused: false option is ignored.

safari_ios.notes: Fires a pair of events: one for private browsing, one for regular browsing.
Fires when toggling in or out of private browsing mode, leaving Safari to the home screen, and returning to Safari from the home screen.
update() will not switch between side-by-side Safari on iPadOS.
